The recommended Python module is:

  http://pypi.python.org/pypi/txLibravatar


Testing
--------

Install dependencies (as root):

  pip install pylibravatar
  apt-get install python-twisted-names python-twisted-web

Clone the module under ~/devel/remote/txlibravatar:

  cd ~/devel/remote/
  bzr branch lp:txlibravatar

and symlink it into place:

  ln -s ~/devel/remote/txlibravatar/txlibravatar.py .

Then run the service:

  ./txlibravatar-test.py

and visit the site at:

  http://localhost:3000/
